solution:
First, let's label the rest of our vertices. [asy]
pair A,B,C,D,E,F,G;

A=(0,0);
B=12*dir(0);
C=20*dir(120);
D=10+B;
E=D+6*dir(0);
F=D+10*dir(120);

draw(A--B--C--cycle);
draw(D--E--F--cycle);

label("A",F,N);
label("B",E+(1.4,0));
label("C",D-(2,0));
label("D",C,N);
label("E",B+(1.4,0));
label("F",A-(2,0));
label("6",.5*(A+B),S);
label("14",.5*(B+C),NE);
label("10",.5*(A+C),SW);
